  "comments": "<p>This coin was minted with frozen dates until 1774, under Christian VII, even if they have the monogram of King Frederik V. More during Frederik V Kingdom there was an devaluation of silver price so the percentage of silver decrease from 0.343 of 1751/1756 to 0.250 of 1761</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Variants</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/69428ba096d73.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/69428ba096d73.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/69428ba08370a.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/69428ba08370a.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/69428ba05da8d.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/69428ba05da8d.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/69428ba06d59b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/69428ba06d59b.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/69428ba0aa102.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/69428ba0aa102.jpg\"></a></p>",
